Hello everyone,
Here I am making this post because since July 1st I have had a bad trip on LSD,
I want to say that before this bad trip I would hit 20 bongs a day and I would do some 1 w.k every two months with some heavy drugs (Taz, coke, LSD, and all the rest)...For 3 years,
now I will tell you how they are going.
a good w.k is waiting for me
on Friday evening everything is going well
one has consumed 5 grams of speed plus all the MD,
Saturday morning after a sleepless night I go to work just in the morning from 9am to 12pm in the afternoon,
continue,
I continued on my side to tap bullets and tap speed,
a colleague is holding the glass with a drop of the lsd bottle for me
I hesitated at first then after I said to myself, let me take it (something I should not have done).
the evening continued normally and the other two so-called colleagues had decided to make us have a great time with the colleagues.....
on this famous beach there were people and one of the two colleagues told us that there is no one looking for shit we are going to beat them....
I thought to myself that the product had to come down because I couldn't fight like that
so I forced myself to resist the product,
the ,the paranoia starts to invade me all while making a mise en scene
the other two colleagues who had not taken anything, began to look for the guys who were angry with us
me being totally lost I told myself it will leave at any moment,
time passes nothing happens.
we leave the beach and go to my place,
I ask them if the guys are following us,
he does not answer,
we arrive at my place and he leaves me all alone at home with my girlfriend who was sleeping...,
I keep on playing my bad all night
impossible to sleep, I think and at the slightest noise I go out with a bat...
the days it rises and I begin to fall asleep because I just realized that there was nothing,
the night passes normally ,
I get up and I am still under the effect of LSD and the rest
I said to myself it's normal
so it was Sunday and the next day I had to work.
the day goes normally
I type some screw then I nap ,
Sunday passes and Monday arrives
I still feel like a mess,
I said to myself it's normal with the car I took....
so at 2 PM I had to take the job
I eat a little and take a big dose of speed to get high...
so I take the car and I go to taff
get to the taff ,as soon as I open the store I start to get dizzy my heart starts to beat at 200 and I feel that I am going to have a fainting spell ,
reassuring me I will buy some snickers bars and some drinks,
after that I go back to the taff and another crisis...
panicked I called my mother.. because the colleague was not the ...
after my mother took me to the doctor
he asks me what I did and I unpack all my bag
and my mother rather took it well in the end you know I was a bit odd..
The doctor told me to wait for the product to come down, it will take a few months, and that's it,
I told her that I had a vision problem
I told her that I had a vision problem
he told me that it was normal too and that he was going to go down,
for my anxiety attacks he prescribed lizanxia an anti axiolitite finally against anxiety ,
I take 1 in the morning and 1 in the evening,
it calms me down but the voices in my head don't stop,
it often gives me a headache...
after this bad I stopped all more nozzle nothing,
my girlfriend didn't understand what happened to me and didn't care
I kicked him out,
